thread.title: Missouri governor indicted on felony invasion of privacy charge

title: Missouri governor indicted on felony invasion of privacy charge
text:
Missouri governor indicted on felony invasion of privacy charge 6:41pm EST - 01:04 
Missouri Governor Eric Greitens was indicted on a felony invasion of privacy charge on Thursday stemming from a probe into an extramarital affair involving the Republican governor. Linda So reports.
